Now, let's talk EQ for a moment. I do believe there is a rule about training people in EQ. Now if someone where to train people and this is seen by a GM, would you condone the trainer telling the GM to &quot;screw himself&quot; if the GM said he was going to Ban him? Would you think that was too harsh a penalty? And if you didn't, maybe someone else did and made a big fuss about it? <br>
