All I am saying is that, in my opinion, you seem to pick which rules and laws are ok to break. That is not justice. Training in EQ will, for the most part, result in some sort of punishment. Either by the GM or fellow players. Breaking the laws or rules in RL will, for the most part, result in some sort of punishment. Either by the police or, in some cases, the citizens themselves. <p>Flubbin<br>
